About Einstein Discovery

Configure Model

Specify the desired outcome (or goal) of your model. You can select an outcome variable to analyze, and the preferred direction (minimize or maximize) is the outcome to take.

Select the outcome that you want to use:
- number fields (measures)
- text fields (categories) with two outcome values
- text fields (categories) with 3â€“10 outcome values

For numeric and binary classification outcomes, select one of the following options:
- Maximize
- Minimize

Show as whole number >= 0 for numeric outcomes.

Specify the name and location of your model:
- Model Name: Accept the default name or enter a new name.
- App: Select the app where you want to save the model.
